Requires Internet, Wi-Fi and compatible smart home devices. Available on Wear OS 3+.

Make daily tasks easier on your smartwatch using just your voice.

November 2023 | Productivity

New Assistant routines for Wear OS

Coming soon, get more done while on the go with Wear OS. Start a custom Assistant routine for any time of day from your smartwatch. Try saying, "Hey Google, commuting to work" and you can navigate to work, check the weather and more.

Android phone required for setup. Internet connection required. Rolling out soon to Wear OS 3+. Google Assistant isn't available in certain languages and countries. Pre-setup is required.
